        <Parent_String>dynamics (mechanics concept) [300056100], mechanics concepts [300072934], physics concepts [300229371], physical sciences concepts [300065446], scientific concepts [300056006], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
